detailed_explanation.title: Overview
bullets: We’ve made a key improvement to the enterprise licensing CSV export to help enterprises better track license consumption of outside collaborators across organizations.

What’s new? – Outside collaborators are now explicitly associated with the organization(s) they contribute to in the license CSV export. – In the CSV’s member roles column, outside collaborator entries will now include a new value in the format: [org]/[repo] .
This improvement makes it easier to determine which outside collaborators are consuming licenses, especially as enterprise owners and billing managers manage budgets across multiple organizations.
To read more, check out our documentation or join the discussion within GitHub Community .
